{"tid":1768943,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 水樹奈奈、茅原實里、坂本真綾、植田佳奈…於2020年迎來40歲的女性聲優一覽","createTime":"2019-12-04T12:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T03:05:33.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"01d0c5c669bfc6ada7fe1fcf76280b2db34c307a","tid":1768943,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T12:39:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/94373/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F94373%2F&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=1e611e52\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/94373/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-6.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F00-6.jpg%3F&h=e4e3279c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>水樹奈奈、茅原實里、坂本真綾、植田佳奈&hellip;於2020年迎來40歲的女性聲優一覽</ins></strong><br />\n作者: 填海紳士 日期: 04/12/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E5%A5%B3%E8%81%B2%E5%84%AA.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%2584%25AA.jpg%3F&h=0dbf66ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在漢語中「年代」是將連續的10年為階段進行劃分的叫法<br />\n而在日本會用「XX代」意指相應歲數的人群，如30代就是30至39歲、40代是40至49歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/%E5%A5%B3%E8%81%B2%E5%84%AA.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%2581%25B2%25E5%2584%25AA.jpg%3F&h=da56a448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n花澤香菜、竹達彩奈、安野希世乃、德井青空、內田真禮等多位女聲優在即將完結的2019年都踏入30歲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>花澤香菜、竹達彩奈、內田真禮&hellip;於2019年迎來30歲的女性聲優一覽</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/76618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F76618&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDUpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=23040e59\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/76618</a><br />\n<br />\n而展望明年我們將踏入21世紀20年代，有日本網友就整理了2020年將迎來40歲的女聲優名單<br />\n<br />\n<strong>在2020年迎來40歲的女聲優</strong><br />\n<br />\n水樹奈奈(出生：1980年1月21日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/%E6%B0%B4%E6%A8%B9%E5%A5%88%E5%A5%88.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25A8%25B9%25E5%25A5%2588%25E5%25A5%2588.jpg%3F&h=ecb6e9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水澤史繪(出生：1980年1月9日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E6%B0%B4%E6%BE%A4%E5%8F%B2%E7%B9%AA.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25BE%25A4%25E5%258F%25B2%25E7%25B9%25AA.jpg%3F&h=0d87bc7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甲斐田裕子(出生：1980年1月14日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E7%94%B2%E6%96%90%E7%94%B0%E8%A3%95%E5%AD%90.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E7%2594%25B2%25E6%2596%2590%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A3%2595%25E5%25AD%2590.jpg%3F&h=241088fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小林沙苗(出生：1980年1月26日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E5%B0%8F%E6%9E%97%E6%B2%99%E8%8B%97.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%259E%2597%25E6%25B2%2599%25E8%258B%2597.jpg%3F&h=56fe8603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n能登麻美子(出生：1980年2月6日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E8%83%BD%E7%99%BB%E9%BA%BB%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%90.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%2599%25BB%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AD%2590.jpg%3F&h=6d3fccd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遠藤綾(出生：1980年2月17日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E9%81%A0%E8%97%A4%E7%B6%BE.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E9%2581%25A0%25E8%2597%25A4%25E7%25B6%25BE.jpg%3F&h=5b998178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坂本真綾(出生：1980年3月31日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/%E5%9D%82%E6%9C%AC%E7%9C%9F%E7%B6%BE.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F%25E5%259D%2582%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%25B6%25BE.jpg%3F&h=3d6f01df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高橋美佳子(出生：1980年5月29日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E9%AB%98%E6%A9%8B%E7%BE%8E%E4%BD%B3%E5%AD%90.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25A9%258B%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590.jpg%3F&h=f0caec2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n植田佳奈(出生：1980年6月9日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E6%A4%8D%E7%94%B0%E4%BD%B3%E5%A5%88.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E6%25A4%258D%25E7%2594%25B0%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E5%25A5%2588.jpg%3F&h=2c51e3d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新井里美(出生：1980年7月4日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%95%E9%87%8C%E7%BE%8E.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BA%2595%25E9%2587%258C%25E7%25BE%258E.jpg%3F&h=5cae7036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n榊原由依(出生：1980年10月13日)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E6%A6%8A%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%B1%E4%BE%9D.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019